headline: Aon’s investments in talent, strong margins set it apart from peers
summary: Investing.com -- Aon’s push to expand its workforce in important sectors like construction, energy and health should give it faster and more durable growth than rivals, Morgan Stanley said, upgrading the insurance broker to Overweight from Equal-weight.
